This paper deals with natural language processing and machine translation, which are typically covered under the arXiv category of Computer Science - Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for extracting parallel sentences from Wikipedia articles. Additionally, the paper uses neural networks and deep learning (DL) for training MT systems. Therefore, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.DL are also likely sub-categories.
